Building Hopecoin

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building Hopecoin QT,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Hopecoin.

Build qt need to install tripartite libraries 
1. libpng-1.6.16
2. qrencode-3.4.4
3. zxing : https://github.com/ClaireDuSoleil/ZebraCrossing.git 

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building hopecoind,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Hopecoin.
